SUMMARY:SeaChange Immersive Installation
DESCRIPTION:SeaChange is an immersive ocean experience created by a team of East Coast artists and surfers dedicated to protecting our oceans. This video and sculpture installation by artists Debrah Pearson Feainn and Jerry Fried is a dynamic environment of 360 video\, scultuptural elements\, environmental sound\, and original music\, presented at 30 minute intervals \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
