SUMMARY:Garden State Art Weekend Kickoff Party: Meet the Artists
DESCRIPTION:Join us at RecRoom to celebrate the start of Garden State Art Weekend\, a statewide celebration connecting communities through art across New Jersey. For three days\, galleries\, studios\, and creative spaces open their doors\, and we’re proud to be part of it! \nOur space is always home to incredible local artwork\, and for this special kickoff\, you’ll have the chance to meet two of the artists behind the pieces. Hang with Jenny Flexner Reinhart and Angelica Dalzon\, whose work is on view throughout RecRoom\, and get a deeper look into their process and inspiration. \nPlus\, artist Charlie Spademan – also featured in our space – will be in his studio right here in the building. Take a quick walk down the hall and say hi. \nWe’ll have wine\, cheese\, and plenty of good conversation – because art is better when it’s shared. Totally free and open to all! \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
