SUMMARY:CreativeMornings: Arlinda MacIntosh of Sophistafunk
DESCRIPTION:CreativeMornings is a free monthly breakfast lecture series for anyone who identifies as creative (yes\, that means you!). With 250+ chapters in 70 countries\, we’re thrilled to host the first & only NJ chapter in Montclair! \nThis month\, our global theme is “Ember” and our speaker is Arlinda MacIntosh. Arlinda McIntosh is best known as the creative force behind Sofistafunk\, a boutique design house known mainly for their voluminous\, picturesque and whimsical skirt collections. Both the Sofistafunk brand as well as Arlinda M\, the private label couture collection\, have been featured on television\, stage\, film\, magazines and periodicals. \n“The loves of my fashionable life: “Big skirts\, DANCE\, Entomology\, Vintage Finery soap bubbles and the fairy tale.” -Arlinda McIntosh \nCan’t wait to see you there! \nShare this:\n				Share on Facebook (Opens in new window)\n				Facebook\n			\n				Share on Bluesky (Opens in new window)\n				Bluesky\n			\n				Share on LinkedIn (Opens in new window)\n				LinkedIn\n			\n				Share on Threads (Opens in new window)\n				Threads\n			\n				Share on Nextdoor (Opens in new window)\n				Nextdoor\n			\n				Share on WhatsApp (Opens in new window)\n				WhatsApp\n			\n				Email a link to a friend (Opens in new window)\n				Email
